{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"installProperties"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"nPspecs","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"pspecs"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UnsafeMutablePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sp"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sp","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafeMutablePointer"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"text":"GParamSpec","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":">?>!)"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All properties should be installed during the class initializer.  It"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is possible to install properties after that, but doing so is not","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"recommend, and specifically, is not guaranteed to be thread-safe vs.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"use of properties on the same type on other threads."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The property id of each property is the index of each ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ParamSpec","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pspecs"},{"type":"text","text":" array."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The property id of 0 is treated specially by ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" and it should not","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"be used to store a "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ParamSpec"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This function should be used if you plan to use a static array of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GParamSpecs"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()"},{"text":". For instance, this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"class initialization:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}]},{"syntax":"C","code":["typedef enum {","  PROP_FOO = 1,","  PROP_BAR,","  N_PROPERTIES","} MyObjectProperty;","","static GParamSpec *obj_properties[N_PROPERTIES] = { NULL, };","","static void","my_object_class_init (MyObjectClass *klass)","{","  GObjectClass *gobject_class = G_OBJECT_CLASS (klass);","","  obj_properties[PROP_FOO] =","    g_param_spec_int (\"foo\", NULL, NULL,","                      -1, G_MAXINT,","                      0,","                      G_PARAM_READWRITE | G_PARAM_STATIC_STRINGS);","","  obj_properties[PROP_BAR] =","    g_param_spec_string (\"bar\", NULL, NULL,","                         NULL,","                         G_PARAM_READWRITE | G_PARAM_STATIC_STRINGS);","","  gobject_class->set_property = my_object_set_property;","  gobject_class->get_property = my_object_get_property;","  g_object_class_install_properties (gobject_class,","                                     G_N_ELEMENTS (obj_properties),","                                     obj_properties);","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"allows calling ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()"},{"type":"text","text":" to notify of property changes:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Langua